Interface List<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - a generic placeholder for any non-primitive Object
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LinkedList

    public interface List<T>
    List interface for simplest ADT of sequentially stored data with changing length.
    Author:
    astjohn

    • Method Summary
